## ğŸ§ª Getting Started

### ğŸ”§ Prerequisites
- Python 3.10+
- PostgreSQL 15+
- Redis

### ğŸš€ Quickstart
```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourname/mdk98.git
cd mdk98

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run the FastAPI server
uvicorn api:app --reload --port 8000

# Access API
http://localhost:8000/docs
```

